Line breaks are a problem for the mouse mode, when you have the move the mouse
all the way to the left. A possible solution is a scrolling lyrics window.
Moving the mouse cursor to the next line automatically is also imaginable in
theory, but not supported by Javascript.

Tablet mode: Tab, gestures (e.g. swipe left/right ) to replace keyboard.

Loading audio from an URL.

Support WaveForm Display:
  Mozilla:
    http://videos-origin.mozilla.org/serv/blizzard/audio-slideshow/#slide1
    http://www.html5multimedia.com/code/ch11/moz-audio-api-waveform.html
  Chrome:
    https://dvcs.w3.org/hg/audio/raw-file/tip/webaudio/specification.html
    http://chromium.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/samples/audio/index.html  
  Libraries:
    https://github.com/grantgalitz/XAudioJS
    http://grantgalitz.org/sound_test/
    http://codebase.es/riffwave/
